    • Class squidpony.squidmath.MultiArrangement extends Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      0L

      • Serialized Fields

        • key

          Object[] key
          The array of keys.

        • value

          squidpony.squidmath.IntVLA[] value
          The array of values.

        • mask

          int mask
          The mask for wrapping a position counter.

        • containsNullKey

          boolean containsNullKey
          Whether this set contains the key zero.

        • first

          int first
          The index of the first entry in iteration order. It is valid iff MultiArrangement.size is nonzero; otherwise, it contains -1.

        • last

          int last
          The index of the last entry in iteration order. It is valid iff MultiArrangement.size is nonzero; otherwise, it contains -1.

        • order

          squidpony.squidmath.IntVLA order

        • n

          int n
          The current table size.

        • maxFill

          int maxFill
          Threshold after which we rehash. It must be the table size times MultiArrangement.f.

        • size
